## Pending: Carbon Builder skill support in verificationSource

### What needs to change (deferred)

Two files need updating to fully support `"carbon-builder"` as a valid `verificationSource`
alongside `"carbon-mcp"`. These changes were implemented and reverted on 2025-07-10.

---

