---

### Why
The `"carbon-builder"` verificationSource value is defined in the port spec
(AGENTIC_CARBON_PR_REVIEW_PORT_SPEC.md § Carbon Verification Rules) but was never
added to the prompt schema or parser. Without it:
- The agent cannot express in its JSON output that it used the skill
- The parser filters out any finding with verificationSource "carbon-builder" as unverified
- The verification badges in comments only render for "carbon-mcp"
